      • mainDescription

        private boolean mainDescription
        A boolean that indicates if this field is the main description of the possible parent record. It is useful in lookup actions to show the description beside the code. I no main description is found for the record, the first non-fixed with field is taken. If no non-fixed field exists, then no description is shown beside the lookup code.
